title: O'NEILL SUPERFREAK 2011/12
description: After the success of the F.U.Z.E entry in the Psycho RG8 series in 2010, O'Neill's Area 52 team developed the same entry for the insane SuperFreak. Now even warmer than it's predecessor the SuperFreak is updated with FluidFlex™ Firewall in the Front Chest and Back. The 2012 SuperFreak keeps the water out and keeps you warm like no other wetsuit ever offered at this price level. One more freak of nature from your friends at O'Neill.
